## Quick start on Streamlit Cloud

1. Fork / clone this repo  
2. Push `app.py` and `requirements.txt` to **main**  
3. In Streamlit Cloud → “New app” → point to this repository  
4. (Optional) add secrets  
   ```toml
   # .secrets.toml
   SMTP_SERVER="smtp.example.com"
   SMTP_PORT="587"
   SMTP_USERNAME="user@example.com"
   SMTP_PASSWORD="***"
